      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ☎️ INBOUND — Vapi Tool Server\nVapi / Retell call these webhook tools **during a live call**.\n\n1. Copy this Webhook's **Production URL** → paste it as the **Server URL** of your Vapi tool(s).\n2. Create 2 tools in Vapi: `check_availability` and `book_appointment` (parameter schemas are in the README).\n3. The reply is auto-formatted the way Vapi expects:\n   `{ \"results\": [ { \"toolCallId\", \"result\" } ] }`\n\n🔁 **For Retell**: change the *Respond to Vapi* node body to\n`={{ { \"result\": $json.result } }}`\n(Retell sends `body.name` + `body.args` — already handled in *Parse Tool Call*.)",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 1760,
        "color": 5
      },
