      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📞 OUTBOUND — Vapi Caller\nInitiates calls through the Vapi API.\n\n▶ Click **Run Outbound Call (Manual)** to test one lead, or\nactivate **Outbound Schedule** for automated calling.\n\nEdit **Define Lead** with your Vapi Assistant ID + Phone Number ID.\nFor bulk calling, replace *Define Lead* with a Lawmatics\n**GET /v1/prospects** + a **Loop Over Items** node.",
        "height": 300,
