    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔑 SETUP\n**Create these credentials (Credentials → Create new):**\n• **Lawmatics** → *Header Auth*: Name = `Authorization`,\n  Value = `Bearer YOUR_LAWMATICS_TOKEN`\n• **Vapi** → *Bearer Auth*: Token = `YOUR_VAPI_PRIVATE_KEY`\n\n**Lawmatics endpoints used** (appointments = “Events”):\n• POST .../v1/prospects → contact / lead\n• POST .../v1/events    → appointment\nVerify field names against your account's API docs; you may need to add\n`event_type_id` / `users`.\n\n⚠️ Sample lead uses a fake number + placeholder IDs, so nothing\ndials until you configure it.",
        "height": 300,
